common.giveFeedback: This is the title of a menu item in the “Help” menu, linking to the GitHub issues for nemo-web.
common.closeModal: This is the label for the close button of modals (e.g., the example selection modal)

editor.examples: This is the label for the button that opens the example selection modal.

navigationBar.documentation: This is the title of a menu item in the “Help” menu, linking to the documentation for Nemo and the rule language.
navigationBar.sourceCodeNemo: This is the title of a menu item in the “Help” menu, linking to the GitHub repository for the Nemo rule engine.

examples.introduction: This is the introductory paragraph shown before the list of example programs in the example selection modal.
examples.title: This is the title of the example selection modal.

footer.thirdPartyLicenses: This is a link in the footer, linking to a file with the collected licenses of all components used in Nemo-web.
